-- EON to Participate in French Hydro-Dam Renewals, Les Echos Says
-- B y   A n d r e a   R o t h m a n
-- 2012-02-06T07:42:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-06/eon-to-participate-in-french-hydro-dam-renewals-les-echos-says.html
EON AG will team up with a group of
French companies named Hydrocop Concessions to provide
hydropower in  France ,  Les Echos  reported, citing EON’s head of
operations in the country, Luc Poyer.  Hydropower is a “strategic area” for EON in France and
the German utility is seeking to manage 2,000 megawatts of the
5,400 megawatts scheduled for renewal, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Rothman in Paris at 
 aerothman@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Kennedy at 
 wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  